Package: shiny.ollama
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Shiny Interface for Ollama
Description: Provides an R Shiny interface to interact with large language models (LLMs) locally using Ollama. This package enables seamless integration of conversational AI capabilities into Shiny applications, offering an efficient and user-friendly interface for local LLM usage.
Author: Indraneel Chakraborty [aut, cre] (<hello.indraneel@gmail.com>)
Maintainer: Indraneel Chakraborty <hello.indraneel@gmail.com>
License: Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/ineelhere/shiny.ollama
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
